      <description>
        
        
        &lt;h1&gt;Bài 8. DOM và Sự kiện – Làm web tương tác&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Mục tiêu&lt;span class=&#34;hx:absolute hx:-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;mục-tiêu&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#m%e1%bb%a5c-ti%c3%aau&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Hiểu &lt;strong&gt;DOM (Document Object Model)&lt;/strong&gt; là gì và vì sao nó quan trọng.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Biết cách &lt;strong&gt;truy cập và thay đổi phần tử HTML&lt;/strong&gt; bằng JavaScript.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Làm quen với &lt;strong&gt;xử lý sự kiện (Event Handling)&lt;/strong&gt; như &lt;code&gt;click&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code&gt;input&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code&gt;change&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Tự tay làm &lt;strong&gt;ví dụ tương tác&lt;/strong&gt; như đổi màu nền hoặc hiển thị thời gian thực.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;1. DOM là gì?&lt;span class=&#34;hx:absolute hx:-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;1-dom-là-gì&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#1-dom-l%c3%a0-g%c3%ac&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Khi trình duyệt tải một trang HTML, nó sẽ biến toàn bộ cấu trúc của trang đó thành &lt;strong&gt;cây DOM (Document Object Model)&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;DOM không chỉ là &amp;ldquo;nội dung&amp;rdquo; mà còn là &amp;ldquo;mô hình dữ liệu&amp;rdquo; để JavaScript &lt;strong&gt;truy cập, sửa đổi, hoặc thêm mới phần tử&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Ví dụ HTML:&lt;span class=&#34;hx:absolute hx:-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;ví-dụ-html&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#v%c3%ad-d%e1%bb%a5-html&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-block hx:relative hx:mt-6 hx:first:mt-0 hx:group/code&#34;&gt;

&lt;div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-html&#34; data-lang=&#34;html&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;body&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &amp;lt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;h1&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;id&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;title&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;Xin chào!&amp;lt;/&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;h1&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &amp;lt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;p&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;class&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;desc&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;Đây là đoạn mô tả.&amp;lt;/&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;p&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&amp;lt;/&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;body&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-copy-btn-container hx:opacity-0 hx:transition hx:group-hover/code:opacity-100 hx:flex hx:gap-1 hx:absolute hx:m-[11px] hx:right-0 hx:top-0&#34;&gt;
